OL,3,CBlair urged to pay back thousands on
OL,4,Cdiscounted designer clothes, files show
OL,6,FPrime minister Tony Blair was advised
OL,7,Fto repay thousands of pounds in
OL,8,Fdiscounts which he received on
OL,9,Fdesigner clothes, according to newly-
OL,10,Freleased official files.
OL,12,FPapers released to the National
OL,13,FArchives show that No 10 officials
OL,14,Frecommended he should pay back more
OL,15,Fthan #7,600 on items bought from
OL,16,FNicole Farhi and Paul Smith.
OL,18,FThe discounts were negotiated by his
OL,19,Fwife Cherie's controversial friend and
OL,20,Fstyle adviser, Carole Caplin, who
OL,21,Fbought clothes for Mrs Blair.
