OL,3,CBlair urged to pay back thousands on
OL,4,Cdiscounted designer clothes, files show
OL,6,FMs Caplin told officials that because
OL,7,Fshe bought the clothes wholesale she
OL,8,Fwas able to to secure discounts of up
OL,9,Fto 60% ` including on items bought for
OL,10,FMr Blair as well.
OL,12,FHowever, officials were concerned that
OL,13,Fsuch large discounts would not be
OL,14,Favailable to ordinary members of the
OL,15,Fpublic.
OL,17,FAccording to the files, between July
OL,18,F2001 to December 2002 the couple spent
OL,19,F#8,021.50 with one designer alone `
OL,20,FNicole Farhi ` when the retail price
OL,21,Fwould have been #20,855.
