OL,3,CBlair urged to pay back thousands on
OL,4,Cdiscounted designer clothes, files show
OL,6,FIt meant the total discount they
OL,7,Freceived came to #12,8343, more than
OL,8,Fthe total amount they spent.
OL,10,FInitially, officials advised that Mr
OL,11,FBlair should repay the discounts he
OL,12,Freceived in full ` around #10,000 `
OL,13,Fand that Mrs Blair should pay back
OL,14,Fhalf the benefits she obtained `
OL,15,F#28,000.
OL,17,FClare Sumner, a No 10 official, wrote:
OL,18,F"We are not arguing that anything has
OL,19,Fbeen done wrong, indeed nothing has.
OL,20,FThe issue is one of public perception."
