OL,3,CBlair urged to pay back thousands on
OL,4,Cdiscounted designer clothes, files show
OL,6,FHowever, after discussions with the
OL,7,Fcabinet secretary Sir Andrew Turnbull
OL,8,Fit was agreed that Mrs Blair did not
OL,9,Freceive any "preferential or
OL,10,Fbeneficial treatment" in her role as
OL,11,Fprime minister's wife.
OL,13,FIt was agreed, however, that the
OL,14,Fsuppliers would in future have to sign
OL,15,Fconfidentiality agreements to ensure
OL,16,Fthere was no incentive for them to
OL,17,Fprovide goods cheaply in order to
OL,18,Fexploit the fact they the prime
OL,19,Fminister's wife wore their clothes.
