OL,6,FBut for Mr Blair, however, officials
OL,7,Fsaid they believed he still should pay
OL,8,Fthe full amount, advising him to write
OL,9,Fcheques for to #1,116 to Paul Smith
OL,10,Fand #6,532 to Nicole Farhi.
OL,12,FMs Sumner wrote: "For you, we still
OL,13,Fthink the simplest thing is to pay for
OL,14,Fyour clothes in full and that Carole
OL,15,Fshould be made aware of this for the
OL,16,Ffuture."
